OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777403484
OL,3,CTwo men arrested following rape in
OL,4,CPlymouth
OL,6,FOfficers have arrested two men
OL,7,Ffollowing a rape in Plymouth at the
OL,8,Fweekend.
OL,10,FDevon and Cornwall Police were called
OL,11,Fto reports of a rape of a woman at a
OL,12,Fresidential property in Sherford, in
OL,13,Fthe early hours of the morning on
OL,14,FSunday 26 April.
OL,16,FThe victim and suspects are believed
OL,17,Fto have first come into contact in the
OL,18,FNorth Hill area of the city before
OL,19,Ftravelling to Sherford where the
OL,20,Fincident occurred.
