OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777403484
OL,3,CTwo men arrested following rape in
OL,4,CPlymouth
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Katy Deer said:
OL,7,F"Our priority has been ensuring that
OL,8,Fthe victim received immediate and
OL,9,Fspecialist support from our officers
OL,10,Fwhile carrying out extensive enquiries
OL,11,Finto the incident.
OL,13,F"Our enquiries have resulted in the
OL,14,Fapprehension of two men, who have been
OL,15,Farrested in connection with the
OL,16,Fincident.
OL,18,F"A 31-year-old man and a 19-year-old
OL,19,Fman, both residing in Plymouth, have
OL,20,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of rape and
OL,21,Fare in police custody.
