OL,3,CTwo men arrested following rape in
OL,4,CPlymouth
OL,6,F"We remain fully committed to
OL,7,Fprotecting women and girls across our
OL,8,Fcommunities and ask that the public
OL,9,Fcontinue to support us ` if you have
OL,10,Fany information that could help with
OL,11,Fthe investigation, please come forward.
OL,13,FAnyone who has any information is
OL,14,Fbeing urged to come forward.
